Package org.forgerock.openam.cts.api.fields

Fields of the Core Token Service.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoreTokenFieldTypes
    Provides the mapping between CoreTokenFields and the type of the value that is associated to that field.
    ResourceSetTokenField
    The ResourceSetTokenField provides a mapping between known ResourceSetDescription fields and the LDAP Attributes that they map to.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    OAuthTokenField
    The OAuthTokenField provides a mapping between known OAuth fields and the LDAP Attributes that they map to.
    SAMLTokenField
    SAMLTokenField defines a mapping between additional fields needed to service the requirements of the SAML token.
    SessionTokenField
    Responsible for describing specific fields of interest in Session Tokens.

Package org.forgerock.openam.cts.api.fields Description

Fields of the Core Token Service. The LDAP backed data store can only store named attributes, therefore each attribute to be stored must be mapped to one of the designated LDAP attributes. The Field enumeration classes provide this mapping. The CoreTokenField being the primary source for the LDAP attribute names.
